        "description": "Generates HLS I-frame variants so Apple TV / AVPlayer clients get native\nscrubbing thumbnails on the transport bar \u2014 no client-side overlay needed.\nOne-time ffmpeg cost per item, then cached.\nIncludes a configurable daily prune scheduled task (orphan removal,\nage-based eviction, optional LRU size cap) so the cache doesn't grow\nunbounded.\n",
